                <td class="p-3 border-b border-slate-100 bg-white">外傷・足マメ</td>
                <td class="p-3 border-b border-slate-100 bg-white font-semibold">キズパワーパッドプラス 大きめ</td>
                <td class="p-3 border-b border-slate-100 bg-white"><a href="https://amzn.to/4crl90i" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored" class="text-sky-600 font-semibold underline">Amazon</a></td>
